data.title: Webb (surname)
data.text:
This article is about the surname "Webb". For the given name, see Webb (given name). For other uses, see Webb (disambiguation).

WebbOriginMeaningWeaverRegion of originEngland, Scotland, Wales, Northern IrelandOther namesVariant form(s)Weaver, Webbe, Webster, Webber, Webe

Webb is an English and Scottish surname meaning weaver of cloth.
